102 dalmatians is a 2000 american family comedy film directed by kevin lima in his live-action directorial debut and produced by edward s. feldman and walt disney pictures . it is the sequel to the 1996 film 101 dalmatians and stars glenn close reprising her role as cruella de vil as she attempts to steal puppies for her " &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; " fur coat yet . close and tim mcinnerny were the only two actors from the first film to return for the sequel , however . the film was nominated for an academy award for best costume design , but lost to gladiator .